786},[2787],{"type":710},{"text":2789,"type":75}," automates gate operations, reducing transaction times by over ",{"text":2791,"type":75,"marks":2792},"85%",[2793],{"type":710},{"text":2795,"type":75},". By instantly identifying assets and verifying load status, the system prevents the \"holding pattern\" common in high-volume distribution centers.",{"type":69,"attrs":2797,"content":2798},{"level":2757,"textAlign":139},[2799],{"text":2800,"type":75},"2. The \"Black Hole\" Between Highway and Warehouse",{"type":1312,"content":2802},[2803,2813],{"type":1315,"content":2804},[2805],{"type":112,"attrs":2806,"content":2807},{"textAlign":139},[2808,2811],{"text":2769,"type":75,"marks":2809},[2810],{"type":710},{"text":2812,"type":75}," A lack of synchronization between the TMS (Transportation) and WMS (Warehouse) results in trailers sitting idle because the dock isn't ready, or vice versa.",{"type":1315,"content":2814},[2815],{"type":112,"attrs":2816,"content":2817},{"textAlign":139},[2818,2821,2823,2827,2829,2833],{"text":2780,"type":75,"marks":2819},[2820],{"type":710},{"text":2822,"type":75}," Terminal acts as a ",{"text":2824,"type":75,"marks":2825},"Digital Bridge",[2826],{"type":710},{"text":2828,"type":75},", integrating directly with TMS and WMS. Its AI-driven ",{"text":2830,"type":75,"marks":2831},"Appointment Module",[2832],{"type":710},{"text":2834,"type":75}," (launched at Manifest 2026) uses real-time visibility to dynamically reschedule slots based on actual truck arrival times, eliminating detention fees and idle dock labor.",{"type":69,"attrs":2836,"content":2837},{"level":2757,"textAlign":139},[2838],{"text":2839,"type":75},"3. Spotter Inefficiency and Task Saturation",{"type":1312,"content":2841},[2842,2852,2873],{"type":1315,"content":2843},[2844],{"type":112,"attrs":2845,"content":2846},{"textAlign":139},[2847,2850],{"text":2769,"type":75,"marks":2848},[2849],{"type":710},{"text":2851,"type":75}," Inefficient move sequences and manual tasking lead to \