r broken trailer tags.",[3966],{"type":149,"attrs":3967},{"color":3568},{"type":1315,"content":3969},[3970],{"type":112,"attrs":3971,"content":3972},{"textAlign":139},[3973,3979],{"text":3974,"type":75,"marks":3975},"Rapid Deployment: ",[3976,3978],{"type":149,"attrs":3977},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":3980,"type":75,"marks":3981},"Full site visibility in 5 business days, compared to 3–6 months for traditional systems.",[3982],{"type":149,"attrs":3983},{"color":3568},{"id":18,"url":18,"linktype":19,"fieldtype":20,"cached_url":18},[1882],{"id":139,"alt":139,"name":18,"focus":139,"title":139,"source":139,"filename":18,"copyright":139,"fieldtype":1105,"meta_data":3987},{},{"id":139,"alt":139,"name":18,"focus":139,"title":139,"source":139,"filename":18,"copyright":139,"fieldtype":1105,"meta_data":3989},{},{"value":1891,"plugin":1892},"yard-roi-calculator-estimate-your-savings-from-ai-powered-yard-automation","all-resources/yard-roi-calculator-estimate-your-savings-from-ai-powered-yard-automation","2025-12-09",-1270,[],"3e6be3c8-836c-4e00-91da-1ee6ae7f3889",[],{"name":3999,"created_at":4000,"published_at":4001,"updated_at":4002,"id":4003,"uuid":4004,"content":4005,"slug":4443,"full_slug":4444,"sort_by_date":4445,"position":4446,"tag_list":4447,"is_startpage":49,"parent_id":1897,"meta_data":139,"group_id":4448,"first_published_at":4449,"release_id":139,"lang":1161,"path":139,"alternates":4450,"default_full_slug":139,"translated_slugs":139},"Networked Yard Intelligence: Orchestrating Multiple Facilities with Predictive Analytics","2026-02-02T23:35:26.901Z","2026-02-02T23:37:14.377Z","2026-02-02T23:37:14.392Z",140843937417246,"33eb0d6f-f6fa-40d8-be58-b071f6ac6b0b",{"_uid":4006,"body":4007,"link":4436,"title":3999,"author":4437,"excerpt":18,"category":1232,"subtitle":18,"component":1883,"seo_image":4438,"seo_title":18,"button_text":132,"cover_image":4440,"seo_noindex":49,"seo_description":18,"background_color":4442},"c014748d-d9fd-4dcd-9280-8f9945c6b0ef",{"type":66,"content":4008},[4009,4022,4031,4039,4073,4082,4090,4142,4352,4361,4369,4419,4428],{"type":112,"attrs":4010,"content":4011},{"textAlign":139},[4012,4017],{"text":3564,"type":75,"marks":4013},[4014,4016],{"type":149,"attrs":4015},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":4018,"type":75,"marks":4019},"For global logistics enterprises, \"visibility\" is no longer enough; the goal is Networked Yard Intelligence. While traditional YMS tools manage sites in silos, Terminal Industries’ Yard Operating System (YOS™) creates a unified data layer across multiple facilities. By leveraging Computer Vision and Predictive Analytics, Terminal enables shippers to orchestrate assets across an entire network, reducing dwell times by 30% and achieving 50%+ throughput gains by treating the yard as a strategic node in the \"Highway to Warehouse\" bridge.",[4020],{"type":149,"attrs":4021},{"color":3568},{"type":69,"attrs":4023,"content":4024},{"level":138,"textAlign":139},[4025],{"text":4026,"type":75,"marks":4027},"How do you achieve multi-site yard visibility?",[4028,4030],{"type":149,"attrs":4029},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":4032,"content":4033},{"textAlign":139},[4034],{"text":4035,"type":75,"marks":4036},"Most organizations suffer from \"blind spots\" between their facilities. Networked Yard Intelligence solves this by aggregating real-time data from every gate and dock into a single command center.",[4037],{"type":149,"attrs":4038},{"color":3568},{"type":1312,"content":4040},[4041,4057],{"type":1315,"content":4042},[4043],{"type":112,"attrs":4044,"content":4045},{"textAlign":139},[4046,4052],{"text":4047,"type":75,"marks":4048},"The Unified Yard Layer: ",[4049,4051],{"type":149,"attrs":4050},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":4053,"type":75,"marks":4054},"Terminal Industries uses AI Computer Vision to create a Digital Twin of every facility in your network. This allows logistics leaders to see global asset distribution (trailers, chassis, and containers) without logging into separate, site-specific instances.",[4055],{"type":149,"attrs":4056},{"color":3568},{"type":1315,"content":4058},[4059],{"type":112,"attrs":4060,"content":4061},{"textAlign":139},[4062,4068],{"text":4063,"type":75,"marks":4064},"Standardized KPIs: ",[4065,4067],{"type":149,"attrs":4066},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":4069,"type":75,"marks":4070},"Instead of disparate data from manual logs, Terminal provides 99.5% accurate data across all sites, allowing for objective benchmarking of carrier performance and site efficiency.",[4071],{"type":149,"attrs":4072},{"color":3568},{"type":69,"attrs":4074,"content":4075},{"level":138,"textAlign":139},[4076],{"text":4077,"type":75,"marks":4078},"Can predictive analytics prevent yard congestion?",[4079,4081],{"type":149,"attrs":4080},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":4083,"content":4084},{"textAlign":139},[4085],{"text":4086,"type":75,"marks":4087},"Predictive analytics transforms the yard from reactive to proactive. By analyzing inflow from the \"Highway\" and capacity in the \"Warehouse,\" Terminal’s YOS™ predicts bottlenecks before they happen.",[4088],{"type":149,"attrs":4089},{"color":3568},{"type":4091,"attrs":4092,"content":4093},"ordered_list",{"order":71},[4094,4110,4126],{"type":1315,"content":4095},[4096],{"type":112,"attrs":4097,"content":4098},{"textAlign":139},[4099,4105],{"text":4100,"type":75,"marks":4101},"Congestion Forecasting: ",[4102,4104],{"type":149,"attrs":4103},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":4106,"type":75,"marks":4107},"The system identifies high-volume arrival patterns and alerts management 2–4 hours before a gate backlog occurs.",[4108],{"type":149,"attrs":4109},{"color":3568},{"type":1315,"content":4111},[4112],{"type":112,"attrs":4113,"content":4114},{"textAlign":139},[4115,4121],{"text":4116,"type":75,"marks":4117},"Autonomous Re-Routing: ",[4118,4120],{"type":149,"attrs":4119},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":4122,"type":75,"marks":4123},"In a networked environment, the YOS™ can suggest re-routing inbound loads to nearby facilities with lower utilization, balancing the load across the network.",[4124],{"type":149,"attrs":4125},{"color":3568},{"type":1315,"content":4127},[4128],{"type":112,"attrs":4129,"content":4130},{"textAlign":139},[4131,4137],{"text":4132,"type":75,"marks":4133},"Proactive Spotter Management: ",[4134,4136],{"type":149,"attrs":4135},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":4138,"type":75,"marks":4139},"By predicting upcoming surges, Terminal can optimize spotter shifts across the network, ensuring labor is where it's needed most before the peak hits.",[4140],{"type":149,"attrs":4141},{"color":3568},{"type":2440,"content":4143},[4144,4178,4213,4248,4282,4317],{"type":2443,"content":4145},[4146,4156,4167],{"type":2446,"attrs":4147,"content":4148},{"colspan":71,"rowspan":71,"colwidth":139,"backgroundColor":139},[4149],{"type":112,"attrs":4150,"content":4151},{"textAlign":139},[4152],{"text":2453,"type":75,"marks":4153},[4154],{"type":149,"attrs":4155},{"color":2499},{"type":2446,"attrs":4157,"content":4158},{"colspan":71,"rowspan":71,"colwidth":139,"backgroundColor":139},[4159],{"type":112,"attrs":4160,"content":4161},{"textAlign":139},[4162],{"text":4163,"type":75,"marks":4164},"Legacy YMS (Siloed)",[4165],{"type":149,"attrs":4166},{"color":2499},{"type":2446,"attrs":4168,"content":4169},{"colspan":71,"rowspan":71,"colwidth":139,"backgroundColor":139},[4170],{"type":112,"attrs":4171,"content":4172},{"textAlign":139},[4173],{"text":4174,"type":75,"marks":4175},"Terminal YOS™ (Networked)",[4176],{"type":149,"attrs":4177},{"color":2499},{"type":2443,"content":4179},[4180,4191,4202],{"type":2446,"attrs":4181,"content":4182},{"colspan":71,"rowspan":71,"colwidth":139,"backgroundColor":139},[4183],{"type":112,"attrs":4184,"content":4185},{"textAlign":139},[4186],{"text":4187,"type":75,"marks":4188},"Data Source",[4189],{"type":149,"attrs":4190},{"color":2499},{"type":2446,"attrs":4192,"content":4193},{"colspan":71,"rows