2,"attrs":5639,"content":5640},{"textAlign":139},[5641],{"text":5642,"type":75,"marks":5643},"Without a standardized operating system, every yard in your network operates as a silo. This leads to hidden costs in detention fees, demurrage, and driver idle time that can fluctuate by 300% site-to-site. Terminal provides the \"Single Source of Truth\" needed to benchmark performance and eliminate these financial blind spots.",[5644],{"type":149,"attrs":5645},{"color":3568},{"type":69,"attrs":5647,"content":5648},{"level":1919,"textAlign":139},[5649],{"text":5650,"type":75,"marks":5651},"2. The Service Reliability Risk",[5652,5654],{"type":149,"attrs":5653},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5656,"content":5657},{"textAlign":139},[5658],{"text":5659,"type":75,"marks":5660},"When the \"Highway\" (TMS) and \"Warehouse\" (WMS) aren't bridged by an intelligent yard layer, small delays at the gate cascade into missed production windows. Terminal’s Agentic AI ensures that the highest-priority loads are moved first, protecting customer SLAs and preventing downstream outages.",[5661],{"type":149,"attrs":5662},{"color":3568},{"type":69,"attrs":5664,"content":5665},{"level":1919,"textAlign":139},[5666],{"text":5667,"type":75,"marks":5668},"3. The Accountability & Governance Risk",[5669,5671],{"type":149,"attrs":5670},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5673,"content":5674},{"textAlign":139},[5675],{"text":5676,"type":75,"marks":5677},"Relying on \"radio chatter\" and clipboards makes it impossible to conduct a clean audit of asset movements or safety compliance. Terminal Industries’ AI Computer Vision creates an impartial, digital log of every event, ensuring that your organization is always audit-ready and compliant with evolving safety standards.",[5678],{"type":149,"attrs":5679},{"color":3568},{"type":69,"attrs":5681,"content":5682},{"level":138,"textAlign":139},[5683],{"text":5684,"type":75,"marks":5685},"Moving Toward \"Networked Maturity\"",[5686,568