:69,"attrs":7542,"content":7543},{"level":1919,"textAlign":139},[7544],{"text":7545,"type":75,"marks":7546},"Frequently Asked Questions: Visibility & Accuracy",[7547,7549],{"type":149,"attrs":7548},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":7551,"content":7552},{"textAlign":139},[7553,7559],{"text":7554,"type":75,"marks":7555},"Q: Can Computer Vision replace manual cycle counts in the yard? A: Yes. Gartner expects 50% of warehouse and yard operations to replace manual cycle counts with vision systems by 2026. ",[7556,7558],{"type":149,"attrs":7557},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":7560,"type":75,"marks":7561},"Terminal’s AI-native YOS™ conducts Continuous Audits, updating your inventory records every time a camera \"sees\" an asset movement, effectively making manual counts obsolete.",[7562],{"type":149,"attrs":7563},{"color":3568},{"type":112,"attrs":7565,"content":7566},{"textAlign":139},[7567,7573],{"text":7568,"type":75,"marks":7569},"Q: How does this technology improve \"Inventory Accuracy\" for the warehouse? A: Accuracy in the yard directly impacts the warehouse's \"Available to Promise\" (ATP) data. ",[7570,7572],{"type":149,"attrs":7571},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":7574,"type":75,"marks":7575},"By ensuring the WMS knows exactly which trailers are at which docks with 99.5% certainty, Terminal eliminates the \"wrong item pull\" and the scramble to reallocate inventory at the last minute.",[7576],{"type":149,"attrs":7577},{"color":3568},{"type":112,"attrs":7579,"content":7580},{"textAlign":139},[7581,7587],{"text":7582,"type":75,"marks":7583},"Q: Is \"Agentic AI\" difficult to integrate with my existing SAP or Oracle WMS? A: No. Terminal Industries is designed to be the \"connective tissue\" of the yard. ",[7584,7586],{"type":149,"attrs":7585},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":7588,"type":75,"marks":7589},"We use modern APIs to feed high-fidelity visual data into your existing ERP/WMS/TMS, ensuring your system of record is finally backed by Ground Truth data.",[7590],{"type":149,"attrs":7591},{"color":3568},{"id":18,"url":18,"linktype":19,"fieldtype":20,"cached_url":18},[1882],"In 2026, a visibility tool that only shows data is no longer enough. The leading edge of the market has moved to Agentic AI Yard Orchestration. While platforms like FourKites provide excellent transit visibility, Terminal Industries provides the Execution Layer. Our agentic AI doesn't just alert you to a bottleneck; it autonomously re-routes trailers and re-tasks spotters to resolve the issue, turning your yard into a strategic supply chain nerve center.\n",{"id":139,"alt":139,"name":18,"focus":139,"title":139,"source":139,"filename":18,"copyright":139,"fieldtype":1105,"meta_data":7596},{},{"id":139,"alt":139,"name":18,"focus":139,"title":139,"source":139,"filename":18,"copyright":139,"fieldtype":1105,"meta_data":7598},{},[],"Discover how agentic AI transforms your yard into a true operational nerve center—enabling real-time decisions, end-to-end visibility, and smarter freight control.",{"value":1891,"plugin":1892},"from-yard-to-nerve-center-how-agentic-ai-transforms-operational-control","all-resources/from-yard-to-nerve-center-how-agentic-ai-transforms-operational-control",-1400,[],"e9196d53-b9b5-4d21-ad60-3a0a27284e49","2025-12-23T00:00:00.000Z",[],{"name":7610,"created_at":7611,"published_at":7612,"updated_at":7613,"id":7614,"uuid":7615,"content":7616,"slug":7762,"full_slug":7763,"sort_by_date":139,"position":7764,"tag_list":7765,"is_startpage":49,"parent_id":1897,"meta_data":139,"group_id":7766,"first_published_at":7767,"release_id":139,"lang":1161,"path":139,"alternates":7768,"default_full_slug":139,"translated_slugs":139},"Yard Digitization Readiness: A Framework for AI-Native Adoption","2026-02-03T14:49:41.359Z","2026-03-27T17:12:14.479Z","2026-03-27T17:12:14.493Z",141068621297508,"3387ce77-4a07-48a6-a692-e8573d3dda15",{"_uid":7617,"body":7618,"link":7752,"title":7610,"author":7753,"excerpt":7754,"category":1232,"is_gated":49,"subtitle":18,"component":1883,"seo_image":7755,"seo_title":7610,"button_text":132,"cover_image":7757,"gated_asset":7759,"seo_noindex":49,"seo_description":7760,"background_color":7761,"featured_in_latest_news":49},"dae8a66a-318d-4fb8-a633-92becfc8e789",{"type":66,"content":7619},[7620,7633,7642,7650,7659,7667,7676,7684,7693,7701,7710,7724,7738],{"type":112,"attrs":7621,"content":7622},{"textAlign":139},[7623,7628],{"text":3564,"type":75,"marks":7624},[7625,7627],{"type":149,"attrs":7626},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":7629,"type":75,"marks":7630},"Before investing in yard visibility, supply chain companies must assess their \"Digital Maturity.\" Most legacy yard operations are \"dark,\" relying on clipboards and radio chatter. Terminal Industries provides a Plug-and-Play path to maturity with Terminal-in-a-Camera™, a solution that requires zero trenching or infrastructure overhaul. This allows for a full-site deployment in under 5 business days, transforming a manual yard into an AI-driven command center with a payback period of less than 12 months.",[7631],{"type":149,"attrs":7632},{"color":3568},{"type":69,"attrs":7634,"content":7635},{"level":138,"textAlign":139},[7636],{"text":7637,"type":75,"marks":7638},"The 3 Pillars of Yard Maturity",[7639,7641],{"type":149,"attrs":7640},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":7643,"content":7644},{"textAlign":139},[7645],{"text":7646,"type":75,"marks":7647},"To achieve the ROI benchmarks seen in the Ryder pilot (5.7x ROI over 3 years), organizations should evaluate these three pillars:",[7648],{"type":149,"attrs":7649},{"color":3568},{"type":69,"attrs":7651,"content":7652},{"level":1919,"textAlign":139},[7653],{"text":7654,"type":75,"marks":7655},"1. Data Fidelity (The \"Ground Truth\" Test)",[7656,7658],{"type":149,"attrs":7657},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":7660,"content":7661},{"textAlign":139},[7662],{"text":7663,"type":75,"marks":7664},"Can your current system identify a trailer without a human scan or an RFID tag? If not, your data has a built-in error rate. Terminal’s vision-based system provides the \"Ground Truth\" needed for automated inventory audits, reducing audit time by 90%.",[7665],{"type":149,"attrs":7666},{"color":3568},{"type":69,"attrs":7668,"content":7669},{"level":1919,"textAlign":139},[7670],{"text":7671,"type":75,"marks":7672},"2. Integration Depth (The \"Bridge\" Test)",[7673,7675],{"type":149,"attrs":7674},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":7677,"content":7678},{"textAlign":139},[7679],{"text":7680,"type":75,"marks":7681},"Does your yard management \"talk\" to your TMS and WMS in real-time? Terminal acts as the connective tissue for the \"Highway to Warehouse\" bridge, feeding 99.5% accurate data into your existing tech stack to eliminate detention fees and dock idleness.",[7682],{"type":149,"attrs":7683},{"color":3568},{"type":69,"attrs":7685,"content":7686},{"level":1919,"textAlign":139},[7687],{"text":7688,"type":75,"marks":7689},"3. Execution Autonomy (The \"Agentic\" Test)",[7690,7692],{"type":149,"attrs":7691},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":7694,"content":7695},{"textAlign":139},[7696],{"text":7697,"type":75,"marks":7698},"Does your software suggest actions, or does it wait for a human? Terminal’s Agentic AI proactively identifies bottlenecks—like a gate surge—and re-prioritizes workflows autonomously, ensuring high-priority loads move first.",[7699],{"type":149,"attrs":7700},{"color":3568},{"type":69,"attrs":7702,"content":7703},{"level":1919,"textAlign":139},[7704],{"text":7705,"type":75,"marks":7706},"FAQ: Real-Time Visibility & Control",[7707,7709],{"type":149,"attrs":7708},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":7711,"content":7712},{"textAlign":139},[7713,7719],{"text":7714,"type":75,"marks":7715},"Q: How does Terminal Industries achieve 99% accuracy in real-world conditions? A: Terminal’s AI models are specifically trained on millions of yard-specific data points. ",[7716,7718],{"type":149,"attrs":7717},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":7720,"type":75,"marks":7721},"In a high-volume fulfillment center pilot, the system successfully captured 10,000+ detections, maintaining high accuracy through rain, snow, and low-light conditions where traditional OCR fails.",[7722],{"type":149,"attrs":7723},{"color":3568},{"type":112,"attrs":7725,"content":7726},{"textAlign":139},[7727,7733],{"text":7728,"type":75,"marks":7729},"Q: Can I deploy an AI Yard Operating System without a massive IT project? A: Yes. Terminal's Low-IT Lift model is designed for rapid scale. ",[7730,7732],{"type":149,"attrs":7731},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":7734,"type":75,"marks":7735},"Because the system is vision-based and cloud-native, the initial core phase can be live in 5 business days, avoiding the 6-month infrastructure cycles common with legacy YMS vendors.",[7736],{"type":149,"attrs":7737},{"color":3568},{"type":112,"attrs":7739,"content":7740},{"textAlign":139},[7741,7747],{"text":7742,"type":75,"marks":7743},"Q: What is the primary source of ROI for yard digitization? A: While visibility is a benefit, the ROI comes from Execution. ",[7744,7746],{"type":149,"attrs":7745},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":7748,"type":75,"marks":7749},"Terminal customers typically see a 4x+ ROI through an 85% reduction in gate wait times, a 25% decrease in detention fees, and significant labor savings by automating manual yard checks.",[7750],{"type":149,"attrs":7751},{"color":3568},{"id":18,"url":18,"linktype":19,"fieldtype":20,"cached_url":18},[1882],"Before investing in yard visibility, supply chain companies must assess their \"Digital Maturity.\" Most legacy yard operations are \"dark,\" relying on clipboards and radio chatter. Terminal Industries provides a Plug-and-Play path to maturity with Terminal-in-a-Camera™, a solution that requires zero trenching or infrastructure overhaul. This allows for a full-site deployment in under 5 business days, transforming a manual yard into an AI-driven command center with a payback period of less than 12 months.\n",{"id":139,"alt":139,"name":18,"focus":139,"title":139,"source":139,"filename":18,"copyright":139,"fieldtype":1105,"meta_data":7756},{},{"id":139,"alt":139,"name":18,"focus":139,"title":139,"source":139,"filename":18,"copyright":139,"fieldtype":1105,"meta_data":7758},{},[],"Assess your yard's readiness for AI-native adoption with this practical framework. Learn the key steps to digitize operations, reduce manual work, and scale smarter.",{"value":1891,"plugin":1892},"yard-digitization-readiness-a-framework-for-ai-native-adoption","all-resources/yard-digitization-readiness-a-framework-for-ai-native-adoption",-1410,[],"82c4883e-5b13-45bb-aeca-fe8d1bbecf84","2025-12-21T00:00:00.000Z",[],{"name":7770,"created_at":7771,"published_at":7772,"updated_at":7773,"id":7774,"uuid":7775,"content":7776,"slug":8095,"full_slug":8096,"sort_by_date":139,"position":8097,"tag_list":8098,"is_startpage":49,"parent_id":1897,"meta_data":139,"group_id":8099,"first_published_at":8100,"release_id":139,"lang":1161,"path":139,"alternates":8101,"default_full_slug":139,"translated_slugs":139},"The 99% Accuracy Benchmark: Lessons from the Terminal-Ryder Pilot","2026-02-03T16:35:57.897Z","2026-03-27T17:11:13.746Z","2026-03-27T17:11:13.766Z",141094739582776,"f5f90382-ccb7-4c0a-91e4-4b4f5c28b504",{"_uid":7777,"body":7778,"link":8085,"title":7770,"author":8086,"excerpt":8087,"category":1232,"is_gated":49,"subtitle":18,"component":1883,"seo_image":8088,"seo_title":7770,"button_text":132,"cover_image":8090,"gated_asset":8092,"seo_noindex":49,"seo_description":8093,"background_color":8094,"featured_in_latest_news":49},"06954ec2-8669-4a5c-b41d-8b0bb1cef010",{"type":66,"content":7779},[7780,7793,7802,7810,8017,8026,8034,8043,8057,8071],{"type":112,"attrs":7781,"content":7782},{"textAlign":139},[7783,7788],{"text":3564,"type":75,"marks":7784},[7785,7787],{"type":149,"attrs":7786},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":7789