oji",{"name":8545,"emoji":8546,"fallbackImage":8547},"bulb","💡","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/emoji-datasource-apple/img/apple/64/1f4a1.png",{"text":8549,"type":75,"marks":8550}," FAQ: Digitizing the Modern Yard",[8551,8553],{"type":149,"attrs":8552},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":8555,"content":8556},{"textAlign":139},[8557,8563],{"text":8558,"type":75,"marks":8559},"Q: What is the fastest way to digitize a large-scale yard network? A: The fastest path is a hardware-agnostic, AI-native platform. ",[8560,8562],{"type":149,"attrs":8561},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":8564,"type":75,"marks":8565},"Terminal’s \"In-a-Camera\" deployment model allows for full site digitization in 5 business days, enabling multi-site operators to scale intelligence across hundreds of yards in a single quarter.",[8566],{"type":149,"attrs":8567},{"color":3568},{"type":112,"attrs":8569,"content":8570},{"textAlign":139},[8571,8577],{"text":8572,"type":75,"marks":8573},"Q: How does Computer Vision handle \"Real-World\" occlusions like rain or dirt? A: Unlike basic OCR, Terminal’s proprietary models are trained on millions of yard-specific data points. ",[8574,8576],{"type":149,"attrs":8575},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":8578,"type":75,"marks":8579},"They are engineered to achieve 99% accuracy even in inclement weather, low light, and with obscured or bent license plates.",[8580],{"type":149,"attrs":8581},{"color":3568},{"type":112,"attrs":8583,"content":8584},{"textAlign":139},[8585,8591],{"text":8586,"type":75,"marks":8587},"Q: Is \"Agentic AI\" just another word for automation? A: No. Automation follows a script (e.g., \"If A, then B\"). ",[8588,8590],{"type":149,"attrs":8589},{"color":3568},{"type":710},{"text":8592,"type":75,"marks":8593},"Agentic AI reasons through variables (e.g., \"Dock 5 is blocked, Spotter A is on break, Trailer B is late—reschedule move to Dock 7\"). It makes the optimal decision in real-time as conditions change.",[8594],{"type":149,"attr